    Use <code>&lt;HeaderTemplate &gt;</code>, <code>&lt;ChildContent &gt;</code> and <code>&lt;SummaryTemplate &gt;</code> to define custom content for Panel component parts.
</RadzenText>

<RadzenText Anchor="panel#expand-collapse" TextStyle="TextStyle.H5" TagName="TagName.H2">
    Expand/Collapse
</RadzenText>
<RadzenText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body1" class="rz-mb-8">
    Use <code>AllowCollapse</code> property to allow expand/collapse and <code>Expand</code> and <code>Collapse</code> callbacks to catch if Panel component is expanded or collapsed.
</RadzenText>
